      <div class="legend-item"><span class="legend-circle" style="background:#e74c3c;width:14px;height:14px;border:2px solid #e74c3c;background:transparent"></span> 衍生路紅＝有規律</div>
      <div class="legend-item"><span class="legend-circle" style="background:#3498db;width:14px;height:14px;border:2px solid #3498db;background:transparent"></span> 衍生路藍＝沒規律</div>
